@startuml External Linking Pattern
!include ../PlantUML/config.cfg

title AgentCode Framework - External Linking Pattern

' === SRS DOCUMENT ===
package "SRS Document" as SRS #LightBlue {
  file "SRS_{Project}_v1.0.0.md"
}

' === SDD DOCUMENT ===
package "SDD Document" as SDD #LightGreen {
  file "SDD_{Project}_v1.0.0.md"
}

' === EXTERNAL DIAGRAMS ===
package "Diagrams (External)" #LightYellow {
  folder "diagrams/" as DiagRoot {
    file "context-diagram.puml" as Context
    file "entity-relationship.puml" as ER
    file "screen-flow.puml" as ScreenFlow

    folder "uc-01/" as UC1 {
      file "uc-01-use-case.puml" as UC1UC
      file "uc-01-screenflow.puml" as UC1SF
      file "uc-01-statediagram.puml" as UC1State
      file "uc-01-sequence.puml" as UC1Seq
      file "uc-01-class-backend.puml" as UC1BE
      file "uc-01-class-frontend.puml" as UC1FE
    }

    folder "uc-02/" as UC2 {
      file "uc-02-use-case.puml"
      file "uc-02-screenflow.puml"
      file "uc-02-statediagram.puml"
      file "uc-02-sequence.puml"
      file "uc-02-class-backend.puml"
      file "uc-02-class-frontend.puml"
    }
  }
}

' === LINKS FROM SRS ===
SRS --> Context : **[Context Diagram]**
SRS --> ER : **[ER Diagram]**
SRS --> ScreenFlow : **[Screen Flow]**
SRS --> UC1UC : **UC01 Use Case**
SRS --> UC1SF : **UC01 Screen**
SRS --> UC1State : **UC01 State**
SRS --> UC1Seq : **UC01 Sequence**
SRS --> UC1BE : **UC01 BE Classes**
SRS --> UC1FE : **UC01 FE Classes**

' === DATABASE & API ===
package "Database (External)" as DB #LightGray {
  folder "db/" as DBRoot {
    file "schema.sql" as Schema
    folder "tables/" as Tables {
      file "uc01_tables.sql"
      file "uc02_tables.sql"
    }
  }
}

package "API (External)" as API #LightGray {
  folder "api/" as APIRoot {
    file "openapi.yaml" as OpenAPI
  }
}

SDD --> Schema : **[schema.sql]**
SDD --> OpenAPI : **[openapi.yaml]**
SDD --> ER : **[ER Diagram]**

' === MARKDOWN REFERENCE FORMAT ===
note as N1 #LightYellow
  **Linking Syntax in Markdown:**

  **Link to PlantUML (not rendered in MD):**
  ```
  [Use Case Diagram](./diagrams/uc-01/uc-01-use-case.puml)
  ```

  **Link to Image (if rendered):**
  ```
  ![UC01](./diagrams/uc-01/uc-01-use-case.png)
  ```

  **Link to code/data files:**
  ```
  [Schema](./db/schema.sql)
  [OpenAPI](./api/openapi.yaml)
  ```
end note

' === KEY POINTS ===
note as N2 #Pink
  **BENEFITS of External Linking:**

  1. **Separation of Concerns**
     - Document = readable text
     - Diagrams = PlantUML source

  2. **Parallel Generation**
     - N agents create diagrams simultaneously
     - No blocking on diagram embedding

  3. **Maintainability**
     - Update diagrams without touching document
     - IDEs render PlantUML from external files

  4. **Consistency**
     - Single source of truth
     - No duplicate diagram code
end note

legend right
  |= Color |= Meaning |
  | <back:#LightBlue>  </back> | SRS Document |
  | <back:#LightGreen> </back> | SDD Document |
  | <back:#LightYellow></back> | PlantUML Diagrams (External) |
  | <back:#LightGray>  </back> | Database/API (External) |
endlegend

@enduml
